eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.repository.model.domain

Class Flow

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.repository.model.domain.AbstractEdge<Node>
      • eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.repository.model.domain.Flow

  • public class Flow
extends AbstractEdge<Node>
    Flow is an edge-like domain object representing data flow between two Nodes. The edge can connect only nodes on the lowest level of the domain hierarchy (e.g. database columns or function parameters).
